         -> SNS Topic: arn:aws:sns:us-east-1:111122223333:EXAMPLE-PRD-Alerts
         -> Email subscribers (default human-readable Grafana message)
       Integration 2 (NEW):
         -> SNS Topic: arn:aws:sns:us-east-1:111122223333:EXAMPLE-PRD-Alerts-JSON
         -> SQS Queue: arn:aws:sqs:us-east-1:111122223333:example-prd-alerts-queue
